reviewtext: I have these all over in my house!  They work great!  I had one for many years that I paid over $50 for but I got my money's worth for sure!  So when I was able to see these on Amazon for less money, I was happy!  They work well, they allow you to plug up many things and move freely.  The cord from the power strip is average length but it does the job!  I would recommend.
